Titolo: Baseball Mogul

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Baseball Mogul is a series of career baseball management computer games created by game designer Clay Dreslough. The product was first published in 1997. The 24th and latest installment is Baseball Mogul 2021. A proprietary database, included with the game, permits play in any season of historical baseball from 1901 to the present. The early Baseball Mogul games are considered to be influential works within the baseball management simulation genre.